Package: ggcomplex
Title: Complex Composite Plots Based on ggplot2 Grammar of Graphics
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Ruidong", "Yang",
           email = "yangruidong1993@163.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = ""))
Description: A toolkit for drawing complex composite plots (heatmaps with
    dendrograms, side annotations, dot plots, circular heatmaps, and more)
    using the ggplot2 layer grammar. It integrates ggtree for tree rendering
    and aplot for subplot alignment, providing a pipeline-style API that is
    both intuitive and extensible.
